Package EvacSim.jme3tools.navmesh

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    A Cell represents a single triangle within a NavigationMesh.
    NavMesh
    A NavigationMesh is a collection of NavigationCells used to control object movement while also providing path finding line-of-sight testing.
    NavMeshPathfinder  
    Path
    NavigationPath is a collection of waypoints that define a movement path for an Actor.
    Plane
    A Plane in 3D Space represented in point-normal form (Ax + By + Cz + D = 0).
